{"data":[{"name":"92:1","price":"1. Par la nuit quand elle voile tout !","arabic":"وَٱلَّيۡلِ إِذَا يَغۡشَىٰ","category":["92 (Al-Lail)","Al-Lail","Surah Al-Lail"],"ayahNumber":6059,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr"},{"name":"92:2","price":"2. Par le jour quand il est dans tout son éclat !","arabic":"وَٱلنَّهَارِ إِذَا تَجَلَّىٰ","category":["92 (Al-Lail)","Al-Lail","Surah Al-Lail"],"ayahNumber":6060,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr"},{"name":"92:3","price":"3. Par ce qui[609] a créé le mâle et la femelle !","arabic":"وَمَا خَلَقَ ٱلذَّكَرَ وَٱلۡأُنثَىٰٓ","category":["92 (Al-Lail)","Al-Lail","Surah Al-Lail"],"ayahNumber":6061,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"[609] Sur la valeur de ce pronom relatif, voir la note précédente, qui renvoyait aux versets 5, 6 et 7 de la sourate Ach-Chams. ","lang":"fr"},{"name":"92:4","price":"4. Vos efforts sont, en vérité, (déployés) pour des desseins divers.","arabic":"إِنَّ سَعۡيَكُمۡ لَشَتَّىٰ","category":["92 (Al-Lail)","Al-Lail","Surah Al-Lail"],"ayahNumber":6062,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr"},{"name":"92:5","price":"5. Celui qui donne (de ses biens) et qui craint (Allah),","arabic":"فَأَمَّا مَنۡ أَعۡطَىٰ وَٱتَّقَىٰ","category":["92 (Al-Lail)","Al-Lail","Surah Al-Lail"],"ayahNumber":6063,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr"},{"name":"92:6","price":"6. Qui croit en la meilleure des récompenses,","arabic":"وَصَدَّقَ بِٱلۡحُسۡنَىٰ","category":["92 (Al-Lail)","Al-Lail","Surah Al-Lail"],"ayahNumber":6064,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr"},{"name":"92:7","price":"7. Nous le mettrons sur la voie la plus facile.","arabic":"فَسَنُيَسِّرُهُۥ لِلۡيُسۡرَىٰ","category":["92 (Al-Lail)","Al-Lail","Surah Al-Lail"],"ayahNumber":6065,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr"},{"name":"92:8","price":"8. Quant à celui qui fait preuve d’avarice, se passe (de la récompense d’Allah),","arabic":"وَأَمَّا مَنۢ بَخِلَ وَٱسۡتَغۡنَىٰ","category":["92 (Al-Lail)","Al-Lail","Surah Al-Lail"],"ayahNumber":6066,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr"},{"name":"92:9","price":"9. et refuse de croire en la meilleure des récompenses,","arabic":"وَكَذَّبَ بِٱلۡحُسۡنَىٰ","category":["92 (Al-Lail)","Al-Lail","Surah Al-Lail"],"ayahNumber":6067,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr"},{"name":"92:10","price":"10. Nous le mettrons sur la voie la plus difficile.","arabic":"فَسَنُيَسِّرُهُۥ لِلۡعُسۡرَىٰ","category":["92 (Al-Lail)","Al-Lail","Surah Al-Lail"],"ayahNumber":6068,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr"},{"name":"92:11","price":"11. Ses biens ne lui seront en rien utiles quand il sera livré (au Feu).","arabic":"وَمَا يُغۡنِي عَنۡهُ مَالُهُۥٓ إِذَا تَرَدَّىٰٓ","category":["92 (Al-Lail)","Al-Lail","Surah Al-Lail"],"ayahNumber":6069,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr"},{"name":"92:12","price":"12. À Nous incombe de guider (les hommes).","arabic":"إِنَّ عَلَيۡنَا لَلۡهُدَىٰ","category":["92 (Al-Lail)","Al-Lail","Surah Al-Lail"],"ayahNumber":6070,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr"},{"name":"92:13","price":"13. À Nous appartiennent la vie dans l’autre monde et la vie en ce bas monde.","arabic":"وَإِنَّ لَنَا لَلۡأٓخِرَةَ وَٱلۡأُولَىٰ","category":["92 (Al-Lail)","Al-Lail","Surah Al-Lail"],"ayahNumber":6071,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr"},{"name":"92:14","price":"14. Je vous mets en garde contre un Feu dévorant,","arabic":"فَأَنذَرۡتُكُمۡ نَارٗا تَلَظَّىٰ","category":["92 (Al-Lail)","Al-Lail","Surah Al-Lail"],"ayahNumber":6072,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr"},{"name":"92:15","price":"15. où ne brûlera que le réprouvé,","arabic":"لَا يَصۡلَىٰهَآ إِلَّا ٱلۡأَشۡقَى","category":["92 (Al-Lail)","Al-Lail","Surah Al-Lail"],"ayahNumber":6073,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr"},{"name":"92:16","price":"16. qui a osé démentir et s’est détourné avec dédain.","arabic":"ٱلَّذِي كَذَّبَ وَتَوَلَّىٰ","category":["92 (Al-Lail)","Al-Lail","Surah Al-Lail"],"ayahNumber":6074,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr"},{"name":"92:17","price":"17. Il ne sera épargné qu’à l’homme pieux,","arabic":"وَسَيُجَنَّبُهَا ٱلۡأَتۡقَى","category":["92 (Al-Lail)","Al-Lail","Surah Al-Lail"],"ayahNumber":6075,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr"},{"name":"92:18","price":"18. qui dépense de ses biens pour se purifier,","arabic":"ٱلَّذِي يُؤۡتِي مَالَهُۥ يَتَزَكَّىٰ","category":["92 (Al-Lail)","Al-Lail","Surah Al-Lail"],"ayahNumber":6076,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr"},{"name":"92:19","price":"19. et ne le fait point pour rendre à quelqu’un la dette d’un bienfait,","arabic":"وَمَا لِأَحَدٍ عِندَهُۥ مِن نِّعۡمَةٖ تُجۡزَىٰٓ","category":["92 (Al-Lail)","Al-Lail","Surah Al-Lail"],"ayahNumber":6077,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr"},{"name":"92:20","price":"20. mais pour être agréable à son Seigneur,[610] l’Altissime.","arabic":"إِلَّا ٱبۡتِغَآءَ وَجۡهِ رَبِّهِ ٱلۡأَعۡلَىٰ","category":["92 (Al-Lail)","Al-Lail","Surah Al-Lail"],"ayahNumber":6078,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"[610] Littéralement : pour le Visage d’Allah : Wajhillah. Voir aussi le verset 272 de la sourate Al-Baqarah.","lang":"fr"},{"name":"92:21","price":"21. Et il sera, assurément, satisfait.","arabic":"وَلَسَوۡفَ يَرۡضَىٰ","category":["92 (Al-Lail)","Al-Lail","Surah Al-Lail"],"ayahNumber":6079,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr"}],"chapter":["92 (Al-Lail)","Al-Lail","Surah Al-Lail","Chapter Al-Lail","Lail","Surah Lail","Chapter Lail","Al Lail","Surah Al Lail","Chapter Al Lail","Surah 92","Chapter 92","The Night","الليل"]}